definitions.definition: Of, to, pertaining to , or used for purposes of conducting trade , commerce , governance , advocacy or other professional purposes.
examples: Please do not use this phone for personal calls; it is a business phone.

definitions.definition: Professional , businesslike , having concern for good business practice.
Supporting business, conducive to the conduct of business.
